label: Military Strength of Nations: An address delivered before the Association of Citadel Graduates, at their meeting in Charleston, 24th November, 1853.
description: Typewritten version of the address entitled "Military Strength of Nations" given to the class of 1853 by Johnson Hagood, The Citadel class of 1847. Subjects include military and political strategies as well as agriculture.
